<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM2.3.11">
<l>kuḻāṅkoḷ pērarakkaṉ kulamvīya muṉintavaṉaik</l>
<l>kuḻāṅkoṭ ṭeṉkurukūrc caṭakōpaṉ ṟerinturaitta</l>
<l>kuḻāṅko ḷāyirattu ḷivaipattu muṭaṉpāṭik</l>
<l>kuḻāṅkaḷā yaṭiyīruṭaṉ kūṭiniṉ ṟāṭumiṉē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Singing these ten in the numerous thousand</l>
<l>clearly spoken by Caṭakōpaṉ from crowded Southern Kurukūr</l>
<l>on the one who destructively hated the numerous big Rakṣasa family</l>
<l>in throngs, o servants join together [and] constantly dance.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
